                "invention-title": [
                    "Method for strengthening oxidizing roasting of neodymium iron boron waste",
                    "一种强化钕铁硼废料氧化焙烧的方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a method for strengthening oxidizing roasting of neodymium-iron-boron waste, which comprises the following steps: mixing the neodymium-iron-boron waste with an additive, and oxidizing and roasting to obtain oxidized neodymium-iron-boron powder; wherein the additive comprises a chlorine-containing compound which can be decomposed at a high temperature to generate chlorine or hydrogen chloride, and the dosage of the additive is 1-20 wt.% of the mass of the neodymium iron boron waste. According to the method, a proper amount of additive is introduced to be mixed with the neodymium-iron-boron waste to be roasted, so that the iron oxidation rate and the rare earth leaching rate are improved, the acid consumption and the use amount of an oxidizing agent and a precipitating agent for recovering the rare earth through a hydrochloric acid optimal solution method are reduced, generation of an NdFeO3 indissolvable phase is avoided, the optimal solution leaching rate of the rare earth is improved, and the recovery cost of the neodymium-iron-boron waste is reduced. In addition, the method is free of introduction of impurity elements, low in additive dosage, low in roasting temperature, short in time, low in roasting energy consumption, small in damage to equipment, easy to operate and suitable for large-scale production."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种强化钕铁硼废料氧化焙烧的方法，所述方法包括以下步骤：将钕铁硼废料与添加剂混合后，氧化焙烧，得到氧化的钕铁硼粉料；其中，所述添加剂包括能够在高温下分解产生氯气或者氯化氢的含氯化合物，所述添加剂的用量为所述钕铁硼废料质量的1wt.％‑20wt.％。本发明通过引入适量的添加剂与钕铁硼废料混合焙烧，提高铁氧化率和稀土的浸出率，从而降低盐酸优溶法回收稀土的酸耗、氧化剂及沉淀剂用量，避免了NdFeO3难溶相的生成，提高了稀土的优溶浸出率，降低了钕铁硼废料的回收成本。而且，本发明的方法无杂质元素的引入，添加剂用量少，焙烧温度低、时间短，焙烧能耗降低，对设备的破坏小，操作简单，适合大规模生产。"
                }
            ]
